---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { INSURANCE_SLUGS } from '../../utils/seo_slugs';

const title = "TMS Insurance Coverage | Medicare, BlueCross, Aetna & More";
const description = "Find out if your insurance covers TMS therapy. Comprehensive guides for Medicare, BlueCross BlueShield, Aetna, Cigna, UnitedHealthcare, and more.";
const insuranceSchema = JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "CollectionPage",
    "name": "TMS Therapy Insurance Coverage",
    "description": description,
    "url": "https://tmslist.com/insurance/",
    "mainEntity": {
        "@type": "ItemList",
        "numberOfItems": INSURANCE_SLUGS.length,
        "itemListElement": INSURANCE_SLUGS.map((item: any, i: number) => ({
            "@type": "ListItem",
            "position": i + 1,
            "name": item.title,
            "url": `https://tmslist.com/insurance/${item.slug}/`
        }))
    }
});
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} schema={insuranceSchema} breadcrumbs={[
    { name: "Home", url: "/" },
    { name: "Insurance", url: "/insurance/" },
]}>
    <main class="min-h-screen">
        <!-- Hero -->
        <section class="relative bg-white border-b border-slate-100 overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-50/60 via-white to-blue-50/40 pointer-events-none"></div>
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[400px] bg-violet-500/5 rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-14 lg:py-18 relative z-10">
                <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-400 mb-8 flex-wrap" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
                    <a href="/" class="hover:text-violet-600 transition-colors">Home</a>
                    <span class="text-slate-300">/</span>
                    <span class="text-slate-700 font-medium">Insurance</span>
                </nav>

                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-6">
                    TMS <span class="text-violet-600">Insurance</span> Coverage
                </h1>
                <p class="text-xl text-slate-500 max-w-3xl">
                    Most major insurance providers now cover TMS therapy. Find your provider below to learn about coverage requirements and authorization.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Quick Info Cards -->
        <section class="py-14 border-b border-slate-100 bg-white">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm flex gap-5 items-start">
                        <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-emerald-50 flex items-center justify-center">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-1">Most Plans Cover TMS</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Medicare, BCBS, Aetna, Cigna, and UnitedHealthcare all cover TMS when criteria are met.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm flex gap-5 items-start">
                        <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0113.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375H8.25m5.231 13.481L15 17.25m-4.5-15H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v16.5c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 00-9-9zm3.75 11.625a2.625 2.625 0 11-5.25 0 2.625 2.625 0 015.25 0z"/></svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-1">Pre-Authorization Required</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Most insurers require prior authorization. Your clinic can typically handle this process for you.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm flex gap-5 items-start">
                        <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-violet-50 flex items-center justify-center">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-violet-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.75 3.104v5.714a2.25 2.25 0 01-.659 1.591L5 14.5M9.75 3.104c-.251.023-.501.05-.75.082m.75-.082a24.301 24.301 0 014.5 0m0 0v5.714c0 .597.237 1.17.659 1.591L19.8 15.3M14.25 3.104c.251.023.501.05.75.082M19.8 15.3l-1.57.393A9.065 9.065 0 0112 15a9.065 9.065 0 00-6.23.693L5 14.5m14.8.8l1.402 1.402c1.232 1.232.65 3.318-1.067 3.611A48.309 48.309 0 0112 21c-2.773 0-5.491-.235-8.135-.687-1.718-.293-2.3-2.379-1.067-3.61L5 14.5"/></svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-1">2+ Failed Medications</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Coverage usually requires documentation of at least 2 failed antidepressant trials.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Major Providers -->
        <section class="py-16">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
                <div class="mb-10">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Major Providers</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-500">Detailed coverage guides for the largest insurance carriers.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <a href="/insurance/medicare/" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-emerald-200 transition-all relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1.5 h-full bg-emerald-500 rounded-l-2xl"></div>
                        <div class="pl-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors mb-2">Medicare</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Covers TMS for treatment-resistant depression nationwide. No referral needed for Part B beneficiaries. Typically 36 sessions approved.</p>
                            <span class="text-emerald-600 font-medium text-sm inline-flex items-center gap-1">View Coverage Guide <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg></span>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/insurance/bluecross-blueshield/" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-blue-200 transition-all relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1.5 h-full bg-blue-500 rounded-l-2xl"></div>
                        <div class="pl-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors mb-2">Blue Cross Blue Shield</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Most BCBS plans cover TMS for MDD with prior authorization. Policies vary by state affiliate. 30-36 sessions typically approved.</p>
                            <span class="text-blue-600 font-medium text-sm inline-flex items-center gap-1">View Coverage Guide <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg></span>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/insurance/aetna/" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-violet-200 transition-all relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1.5 h-full bg-violet-500 rounded-l-2xl"></div>
                        <div class="pl-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-violet-600 transition-colors mb-2">Aetna</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Covers TMS as medically necessary for MDD after 2+ failed medication trials. Prior authorization required. Up to 36 sessions.</p>
                            <span class="text-violet-600 font-medium text-sm inline-flex items-center gap-1">View Coverage Guide <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg></span>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/insurance/cigna/" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-amber-200 transition-all relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1.5 h-full bg-amber-500 rounded-l-2xl"></div>
                        <div class="pl-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-amber-600 transition-colors mb-2">Cigna</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Covers rTMS for major depression with prior auth. Requires documented failure of 2+ antidepressants in the current episode.</p>
                            <span class="text-amber-600 font-medium text-sm inline-flex items-center gap-1">View Coverage Guide <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg></span>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/insurance/united-healthcare/" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-sky-200 transition-all relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1.5 h-full bg-sky-500 rounded-l-2xl"></div>
                        <div class="pl-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-sky-600 transition-colors mb-2">UnitedHealthcare</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">UHC covers TMS for treatment-resistant MDD. Prior authorization and clinical documentation required. 30-36 sessions standard.</p>
                            <span class="text-sky-600 font-medium text-sm inline-flex items-center gap-1">View Coverage Guide <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg></span>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/insurance/tricare/" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-rose-200 transition-all relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1.5 h-full bg-rose-500 rounded-l-2xl"></div>
                        <div class="pl-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-rose-600 transition-colors mb-2">Tricare</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Covers TMS for active duty, retirees, and dependents. Referral from PCM required. Both standard and deep TMS protocols covered.</p>
                            <span class="text-rose-600 font-medium text-sm inline-flex items-center gap-1">View Coverage Guide <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg></span>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- All Providers Grid -->
        <section class="py-16 bg-white border-t border-slate-100">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
                <div class="mb-10">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">All Coverage Guides</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-500">State-specific policies, regional carriers, and government programs.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
                    {INSURANCE_SLUGS.filter(item => !['medicare', 'bluecross-blueshield', 'aetna', 'cigna', 'united-healthcare', 'tricare'].includes(item.slug)).map(item => (
                        <a href={`/insurance/${item.slug}/`} class="group bg-slate-50 hover:bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-slate-100 hover:border-violet-200 hover:shadow-sm transition-all flex items-center justify-between gap-3">
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800 group-hover:text-violet-600 transition-colors">{item.title.replace(' TMS Coverage', '').replace(' TMS Rules', '').replace(' TMS Policy', '').replace(' TMS', '').replace(' Coverage for TMS', '')}</h3>
                            </div>
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-300 group-hover:text-violet-400 shrink-0 transition-colors" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.25 4.5l7.5 7.5-7.5 7.5"/></svg>
                        </a>
                    ))}
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- CTA Section -->
        <section class="py-16">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-600 to-indigo-700 rounded-3xl p-10 md:p-14 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iNjAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjAiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCA2MCA2MCIgeG1sbnM9Imh0dHA6Ly93d3cudzMub3JnLzIwMDAvc3ZnIj48ZyBmaWxsPSJub25lIiBmaWxsLXJ1bGU9ImV2ZW5vZGQiPjxnIGZpbGw9IiNmZmYiIGZpbGwtb3BhY2l0eT0iLjA1Ij48cGF0aCBkPSJNMzYgMzRoLTJ2LTRoMnYtNGg0djRoMnY0aC0ydjRoLTR6Ii8+PC9nPjwvZz48L3N2Zz4=')] opacity-30"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Not sure if you're covered?</h2>
                        <p class="text-violet-100 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">Take our quick eligibility quiz to find out if you might qualify for insurance-covered TMS therapy, or search for a clinic near you that offers free insurance verification.</p>
                        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
                            <a href="/quiz/am-i-a-candidate/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white text-violet-700 font-semibold px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl hover:bg-violet-50 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-violet-900/20">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.879 7.519c1.171-1.025 3.071-1.025 4.242 0 1.172 1.025 1.172 2.687 0 3.712-.203.179-.43.326-.67.442-.745.361-1.45.999-1.45 1.827v.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-9 5.25h.008v.008H12v-.008z"/></svg>
                                Take the Eligibility Quiz
                            </a>
                            <a href="/near-me/tms-therapy/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-violet-500/20 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl hover:bg-violet-500/30 transition-colors border border-white/20">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1115 0z"/></svg>
                                Find a Clinic Near You
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SEO Content -->
        <section class="py-16 bg-white border-t border-slate-100">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-6">Understanding Insurance Coverage for TMS Therapy</h2>
                <div class="prose prose-slate prose-lg max-w-none">
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">Transcranial Magnetic Stimulation (TMS) has been FDA-cleared since 2008 for treating major depressive disorder, and insurance coverage has expanded significantly since then. Today, most major commercial insurers and government programs — including Medicare and many state Medicaid plans — provide coverage for TMS when specific clinical criteria are met.</p>

                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mt-10 mb-4">What Are the Typical Requirements for Coverage?</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">While policies vary by insurer and plan, most require the following before approving TMS therapy:</p>
                    <ul class="text-slate-600 space-y-2 mb-6 list-disc pl-5">
                        <li>A confirmed diagnosis of major depressive disorder (MDD)</li>
                        <li>Documentation of at least 2 failed antidepressant trials at adequate dose and duration during the current episode</li>
                        <li>Prior authorization from the insurance carrier</li>
                        <li>Treatment administered by a qualified provider using an FDA-cleared device</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mt-10 mb-4">How Many Sessions Are Covered?</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">A standard course of TMS consists of 36 sessions delivered over approximately 7-9 weeks. Most insurers approve 30-36 initial sessions. Some plans also cover maintenance sessions if the patient responds well to the initial course but experiences symptom recurrence.</p>

                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mt-10 mb-4">What If My Insurance Denies Coverage?</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">If your initial request is denied, you have the right to appeal. Many TMS clinics have dedicated insurance coordinators who can assist with the appeals process. Common reasons for denial include incomplete documentation or not meeting the medication failure requirement. A well-documented appeal with supporting medical records often results in approval.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
